      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET I AM (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind I'm Honey (22.32) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can go on with it. SPRING QUIZ (1) was game in defeat off a low draw at the latest outing, finishing third and beaten 1.1 lengths (22.23) behind Annie's Regret at Ballarat. Bold showing expected. PAW BASTOW (5) lines up here off a comfortable win at Traralgon after jumping from box 2 (20.04). Has a tricky draw to overcome and will need a clean break. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Significant danger. PAW MURBELLA (6) is a last start winner who rates one of the chances again.",
